{"tid":1063772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【又黎多單】屯公貨櫃車撞壆拋出司機 貨櫃翻倒封雙線","createTime":"2019-03-16T04:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T05:34:40.000Z","uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"86d27b2b565c84c3a13c6518afc1836e2625d64e","tid":1063772,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T04:35:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190316/large/1552709706_a650.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190316%2Flarge%2F1552709706_a650.jpg&h=a83c0bb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上午11時45分，警方接報屯門皇珠路入龍鼓灘方向有貨櫃車翻側，司機跌出車外重傷。現場所見，貨櫃車車頭毀爛，一人倒卧地上重傷。貨櫃箱則翻倒到對面線，橫封兩條行車線。<br />\n讀者蔡小姐住在附近大廈，事發時聽到「嘭」聲巨響，望出去見到貨櫃車翻側，司機倒卧地上，其他駕駛者落車查看。蔡小姐說，受傷司機似乎不清醒，而來回行車線頓時擠塞。她目測貨櫃車的煞車痕約30米。"},{"pid":"2222565eb3eff48f209134d4c34783ef1b4a3074","tid":1063772,"uid":86,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T04:47:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a9c4f113fd2fd9d8bac3547a9667958252ef4a7","tid":1063772,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T04:47:52.000Z","msg":"又飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0542f23498fdaf1291a99d81da186a7285fb5d66","tid":1063772,"uid":132713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T05:34:40.000Z","msg":"點解可以炒成咁"}]}